    "body": "Something like this?\n\n``` diff\ndiff --git a/OpenRA.Game/Network/Order.cs b/OpenRA.Game/Network/Order.cs\nindex a482c2d..f402597 100644\n--- a/OpenRA.Game/Network/Order.cs\n+++ b/OpenRA.Game/Network/Order.cs\n@@ -64,7 +64,8 @@ public sealed class Order\n\n                public static Order Deserialize(World world, BinaryReader r)\n                {\n-                       switch (r.ReadByte())\n+                       var magic = r.ReadByte();\n+                       switch (magic)\n                        {\n                                case 0xFF:\n                                        {\n@@ -98,7 +99,10 @@ public static Order Deserialize(World world, BinaryReader r)\n                                        }\n\n                                default:\n-                                       throw new NotImplementedException();\n+                                       {\n+                                               Log.Write(\"debug\", \"Received unknown order with magic {0}\", magic);\n+                                               return null;\n+                                       }\n                        }\n                }\n```\n"
